Module detection
Package fr.project.detection.methodVisitor

Class MyMethodVisitor

java.lang.Object
org.objectweb.asm.MethodVisitor
fr.project.detection.methodVisitor.MyMethodVisitor
public class MyMethodVisitor
extends org.objectweb.asm.MethodVisitor
A visitor to visit a method of a .class file. It contains observers that can react when the visitor detects some features.
Author:
CHU Jonathan

      Parameters:
      methodVisitor - - a MethodVisitor you want to link with
      observers - - a list of FeatureObserver you want to link with
      methods - - a list of Method
      lambdaCollector - - a LambdaCollector object
      myMethod - - an object that represents the method you are visiting
      ownerClass - - the class that contains the method myMethod
      exceptions - - all the exceptions thrown by the class
